-- Saudi Police Arrest Nine Men Behind Qatif Shooting, SPA Says
-- B y   M o u r a d   H a r o u t u n i a n
-- 2012-01-24T14:39:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-24/saudi-police-arrest-nine-men-behind-qatif-shooting-spa-says.html
Saudi Arabian police last night
arrested nine citizens allegedly behind shooting incidents
earlier this month in the Shiite area of Qatif, the official
 Saudi Press Agency  reported.  Saudi police arrested the men after raiding “a hideout in
Qatif Province,” SPA said, citing an unidentified spokesman for
the Ministry of Interior. Three policemen were injured on Jan.
14 and 18 when gunmen opened fire on a police patrol in the oil-
rich area, the Riyadh-based news service said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mourad Haroutunian in Riyadh at 
 mharoutunian@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
